 a further adoption of clinical prediction models by providing doctors\nwith intuitions to better understand the reasoning of, usually, black-box AI\nclinical solutions, and make more reasonable and data-driven decisions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 20 Aug 2021 09:03:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-08-25"}
